# Nurul Hikmah School App — Core Stack

## Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Backend | Laravel 12, PHP 8.3+, MySQL 8.0, Sanctum |
| Cache | **File cache only** — hosting does not support Redis |
| Frontend | React 18+, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind v4 |
| UI | Radix UI primitives via shadcn/ui (`src/components/ui/`) |
| Forms | Zod schemas in `src/schemas/` |
| Data fetching | TanStack Query v5 in `src/hooks/` |
| PWA | Workbox — offline-first, cache API responses |

## Constraints

- **NO Redis** — use `CACHE_STORE=file` (or `database`). Never add Redis dependencies.
- UI text: **Bahasa Indonesia**. Code/comments: English.
- Mobile-first responsive design — rule `responsive-mobile-web.mdc`; skill `tailwindcss-mobile-first`.

## Architecture

```
Frontend (PWA) ── TanStack Query ──► Laravel API (Sanctum)
                      │                    │
                 Zod validation      Repository + File Cache
                                           │
                                      MySQL (indexed)
```

